{"tid":670272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"座椅放鉛筆　國中生屁股被插進15公分","createTime":"2018-05-19T08:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T11:39:17.000Z","uid":1121,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7b46c88a38ff14ab2a90f94bf6b24b2c7329bab0","tid":670272,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:16:45.000Z","msg":"學生惡作劇將鉛筆插在座椅上，同學沒注意到一屁股坐下去，讓鉛筆插入屁股15公分。據《都市快報》報導，17日下午，中國浙江一名14歲學生小A(化名)，上學中跟同學一起玩，而同學惡作劇將削尖的鉛筆立在小A椅子上，小A沒注意到一坐，鉛筆深深戳進小A屁股裡。事情發生後學校立即將小A送往醫院，醫生指出鉛筆幾乎是緊貼著直腸進去的，差不多和直腸平行，而旁邊就是膀胱和尿道，差點戳破腸子。 17日晚間，醫生為小A取出了鉛筆，目前，小A還在醫院裡觀察治療，預定明天就可出院回家。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"70c8d539467ae7e108da856fc41aca9cd6cfa1dd","tid":670272,"uid":140776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:17:24.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c784c5b3f41e9a6700a3bf54e0790c1ec4f7e6","tid":670272,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:17:53.000Z","msg":"好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86541aa73433835051f81a608506a36b6cb0dcc","tid":670272,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45c784c5b3f41e9a6700a3bf54e0790c1ec4f7e6","tid":670272,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:17:53.000Z","msg":"好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:55:53.000Z","msg":"0仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd6c52bf1fdad1de7775ce59c75a9358361f3ec","tid":670272,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T09:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dfd73945de463619253a5f29c63112264551a3f","tid":670272,"uid":8767,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19